function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	-- Explode Shrine
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, 16)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, EG_WIN_EXPLODE)
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.1)
	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		local allMobActors = Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_ALL_MOBS)
		-- Spawn super and knock back people from the spawn location
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(ID_SPAWNER_SUPER_ELITE)	
		for i, actorId in ipairs(allMobActors) do
			Hydra.ActorKill(actorId)
		end
		
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_PROTECTION, "DISPERSE", ID_SPAWNER_SUPER_ELITE)	
	end
	
end

local function updateChannelSpawner(idNewChannelSpawner)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCurrentChannelSpawner) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idCurrentChannelSpawner)
	end
	
	idCurrentChannelSpawner = idNewChannelSpawner
	
	if Hydra.PrefabScopedActorGroupGetCount(PSAG_CHANNELERS) == 0 then
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idCurrentChannelSpawner)
	end
	
end
